# READING_ORDER.md

<!-- INSTRUCTION: Boot sequence for any AI executor or human entering this repo. Read in the order listed. Each step has a purpose; do not skip without explicit reason. -->

1. `<repo-root>/REPO_PASSPORT.md` - front-door contract.
2. `<repo-root>/.claude/MASTER.md` - repo-scope authority and per-repo declarations.
3. Authority docs declared in passport section 3, "Authority order" - read in declared order.
4. `<repo-root>/ops/agents/packets/active/` - currently in-flight packets.
5. `<repo-root>/ops/agents/packets/blocked/` - currently blocked packets.
6. Most recent `<repo-root>/ops/agents/handoffs/<latest>-handoff.md` - most recent closeout.
7. `<canonical platform repo>/.claude/PLATFORM/PROTOCOLS_AND_NOMENCLATURE.md` - framework conventions when work is cross-repo, skeleton-touching, or convention-touching.

